[[math]]
[[antithetical_notions_opposites_and_extremes]]
[[geometrical_line_framework_for_examining_and_comparing_antithetical_notions]]
An equal distribution of quantity over the space of another quantity is said to be an even case: in which
division is embarked in, and the retainer is just a composition of the slice, and as such, the remainder stays
at 0; albeit for the other case, odd it is. 
